Deer:

1. Import the files
2. Put the Deer_notMoving2 in the scene
3. In deer_walks and deer_idle go to animation tab and choose 'loop time' and 'loop position'
4. In Assets right click and create Animator
5. Drag the animations to animator, as an entry make 'idle'
6. Right click on 'idle' and 'create transition'. Do that with the rest
7. Click on the transition arrow and mess around with a timeline in the inspector